    ],
    "summary": "Create Jira tickets for a single run",
    "description": "Create Jira Epic, Stories, and Tasks for the given ``run_id``. Requires that the PRD has already been published to Confluence. Uses the CrewAI delivery crew for intelligent ticket creation.",
